Title: Silent Symphony
Plot: Alex helps Hailey figure out an easy way to make money, while back at the symphony hall, an older musician collapses when Rodrigo pushes him too hard. After being humiliated by Rodrigo's assistant, Hailey lets off a lifetime of steam, and is caught off guard when Rodrigo makes her an offer.
ParentalRatingReason: Lightbox Provisional Classification. Official NZ Rating To Be Confirmed.
